Uncle Boonmee Who Can Recall His Past Lives;;61;;89;;NC;;Afflicted with kidney disease, Uncle Boonmee (Thanapat Saisaymar) is preparing himself for death. He has assembled his relatives in the countryside, convinced he will die within a few days. The ghost of his wife appears and offers guidance on his journey into the beyond, while his estranged son materializes in the guise of a jungle creature. Surrounded by his loved ones, Uncle Boonmee reflects on memories of his past lives, and he decides he must visit a special place before he goes.;;Fantasy;;Apichatpong Weerasethakul;;2011;;Sakda Kaewbuadee,Jenjira Pongpas,Thanapat Saisaymar,Natthakarn Aphaiwonk,Geerasak Kulhong,Wallapa Mongkolprasert,Kanokporn Tongaram,Samud Kugasang;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/uncle_boonmee